dcterms:description: An OpenAI Gym environment where a pole is attached to a cart by an un-actuated joint, which is moving along a frictionless track. The goal is to prevent the pendulum from falling over, with a reward of +1 for each time step the pole remains upright.
dcterms:title: CartPole-v1

dcterms:description: An OpenAI Gym environment where the landing pad is located at coordinates (0,0). The goal is to land safely on the landing pad with zero speed, with various actions leading to different rewards.

dcterms:description: A customized environment for a Markov Decision Process (MDP) consisting of a maze with an 8x8 cell structure. The agent must navigate through free cells to reach a target cell, with rewards based on the path taken.
dcterms:title: Maze Traversal
